                Algorithm for egusi soup
Step1: identify items
Step2: how to get items
Step3: where to get items 
Step4: budget needed for step2 and step3
Step5: means to implement step4
Step6: Goback home 
Step7: enter kitchen
Step8: get cooking utensils
Step9: cut/wash meat
Step10: season and steam meat 
Step11: cook the meat
Step12: get a new pot
Step13: put water and otheringerdients
Step14: put the egusi inside the pot and leave to boil
Step15: cut your vegetable (ugwu)
Step16; put the vegetable inside the soup and leave for some seconds
Step17: bring it down and dish 
